## 5. Event Bus — CUSTOM_EVENTS

```ts
OPENED_CHEST          // payload: Chest
ENEMY_DESTROYED       // payload: none
PLAYER_DEFEATED       // payload: none
PLAYER_HEALTH_UPDATED // payload: PlayerHealthUpdated { currentHealth, previousHealth, type }
SHOW_DIALOG           // payload: string
DIALOG_CLOSED         // payload: none
BOSS_DEFEATED         // payload: none
SPELL_CAST            // payload: { spellId, slotIndex }
MANA_UPDATED          // payload: { current, max }
ELEMENT_CHANGED       // payload: ElementChangedData { element }
```

**Pattern:** Subscribe in `create()` / `init()`, always unsubscribe in `SHUTDOWN` event handler.

```ts
EVENT_BUS.on(CUSTOM_EVENTS.EXAMPLE, this.#handler, this);
this.events.once(Phaser.Scenes.Events.SHUTDOWN, () => {
  EVENT_BUS.off(CUSTOM_EVENTS.EXAMPLE, this.#handler, this);
});
```

