## 6. Scene Flow

```
PreloadScene
  └─► GameScene (receives LevelData: { level, roomId, doorId })
        ├─► launches UIScene (HUD overlay, always alongside GameScene)
        └─► can launch RadialMenuScene (pauses GameScene while open)
  └─► GameOverScene (on player death)
```

`GameScene` is restarted (with new `LevelData`) every time the player exits to a different **level** (e.g. DUNGEON_1 → WORLD). Room transitions *within* the same level are handled in-place (camera + player tween) without restarting the scene.

