## 8. Player

`src/game-objects/player/player.ts` extends `CharacterGameObject`.

**Key components attached:**
- `animationComponent` — plays named animations like `IDLE_UP`, `RUN_LEFT`
- `lifeComponent` — current/max HP
- `manaComponent` — current/max mana, regen, `consume(n)`
- `speedComponent`
- `directionComponent`
- `stateMachine` — see §9
- `spellCastingComponent` — see §10
- `weaponComponent` (sword, used for melee — still present but spell system is primary)

**Controls (KeyboardComponent):**
- Arrow keys — movement
- `Z` — cast spell slot 1 (FireBolt / EarthBolt depending on element)
- `X` — cast spell slot 2 (FireArea) / lift-throw objects
- `3` key with EARTH element — cast EarthWall (handled directly in `GameScene.#updateEarthWallSpell`)
- Hold `Z` with FIRE element — channels FireBreath (handled directly in `GameScene.#updateFireBreathChanneling`)
- Tab/radial key — open RadialMenuScene to switch element
- `F2` — toggle hitbox debug
- `Enter` in menus

