## 9. State Machine (CharacterGameObject)

All characters use `StateMachine` composed of states from `CHARACTER_STATES`:

```ts
IDLE_STATE | MOVE_STATE | BOUNCE_MOVE_STATE | HURT_STATE | DEATH_STATE
LIFT_STATE | OPEN_CHEST_STATE | IDLE_HOLDING_STATE | MOVE_HOLDING_STATE
THROW_STATE | ATTACK_STATE | HIDDEN_STATE | TELEPORT_STATE
PREPARE_ATTACK_STATE | CASTING_STATE
```

Transitions: call `character.stateMachine.setState(CHARACTER_STATES.X)`.

